@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist
@token = 1774545626897|test@example.com|user

### Obtener todos los items (sin filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener items filtrados por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/?estado=pendiente
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener items filtrados por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/?tipo=pelicula
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener items filtrados por estado y tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/?estado=completado&tipo=serie
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un item específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/123456
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo item
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "titulo": "Matrix",
    "tipo": "pelicula",
    "genero": "Ciencia ficcion",
    "rating": 9,
    "estado": "pendiente",
    "coverUrl": "https://example.com/matrix.jpg",
    "notas": "Clasico imperdible"
}

### Actualizar un item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1774546194410
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "estado": "visto",
    "rating": 10,
    "notas": "Excelente pelicula"
}

### Eliminar un item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/123456
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
